@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #e6f0ff;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 70px;
        }

        .page-header {
            background-color: #4d94ff;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .page-header h1 {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
                font-family: 'Verdana', sans-serif;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        .content-section {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

            .content-section h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #003366;
            }

            .content-section p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .content-section ul {
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

                .content-section ul li {
                    font-size: 1.2rem;
                    margin-bottom: 10px;
                }

        .footer {
            background-color: #4d94ff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 -4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="page-header">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p>At Employee Management System, we value your privacy and strive to protect your personal information. Below are the guidelines on how we handle your data.</p>
    </section>


    <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>Your privacy is extremely important to us. This policy outlines the information we collect, how we use it, and the measures we take to safeguard it.</p>

        <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect the following information to ensure efficient employee management and support:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Personal information such as full name, email address, and contact details</li>
            <li>Employee ID and job-related data</li>
            <li>Work performance data for reviews and performance tracking</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>The information we collect is used for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Managing employee profiles and job details</li>
            <li>Tracking performance and conducting reviews</li>
            <li>Organizing holiday schedules and leave requests</li>
            <li>Ensuring security and providing personalized access to the system</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Data Security</h3>
        <p>We implement strong security measures to protect your data. We ensure that all personal and sensitive data is stored securely and is not shared with third parties without consent.</p>

        <h3>Data Retention</h3>
        <p>We retain your data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. We comply with applicable data protection laws and regulations.</p>

        <h3>Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. For any such requests, please reach out to our support team.</p>
    </section>


    <section class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Employee Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
